{"tid":370473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【天鴿襲港】杏花邨停車場水浸沒頂 車主叫苦　","createTime":"2017-08-23T05:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T05:11:08.000Z","uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afa375e4acaaf4f11916db7fcb5b714a3575e1dd","tid":370473,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"杏花邨停車場，在天鴿襲港期間成重災區，水浸沒頂，整個停車場出入口完全被水浸淹。據悉，停車場內有30多部車輛，有車主前來取車，才知連停車場入口也進不了。車主顯得非常無奈，「邊有人通知吖！自己落嚟想攞車先知，落嚟已係咁（浸晒），唔好再問我啦，靚唔靚車有乜分別？」他指以前從未試過。<br />\n<br />\n街坊溫先生表示，他今早與家人出外吃早餐，因為水浸回不了家，沿途溜逛，經過赫見水浸車場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57116621&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57116621%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170823&d=HTQbVdZbBIArdKwCPeMvPbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a34fa548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57116621%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170823&h=b47a677e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57116621&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170823</a>"},{"pid":"be605abbce457bd7435fc53a05337b8162b50ab2","tid":370473,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:11:08.000Z","msg":"有無得追究停車場管理公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}